Challenges in Cloud Service Enablement (Preview → GA)

Context

Adoption of new cloud services/features during Preview (pre-GA)
Managed via Terraform Enterprise (TFE)

Challenges

Immature Features: Limited stability, documentation, and support
TFE Gaps: Required resources/providers not fully available in TFE
Provider Dependency: Coordination needed with **Google for access, quotas, fixes
Frequent Changes: APIs/configs evolve before GA → rework required
Higher Effort: Extra testing, validation, and monitoring overhead

Impact

Slower delivery timelines
Increased engineering effort
Higher risk to production readiness

